caller_intent: The caller (William) is seeking clarification about a bill from Utica National Insurance Group, believing he may have already paid his premium for a property in Linwood under his name (William and Mary).
summary: William contacted Alliance Insurance Services after receiving a bill from Utica National Insurance Group, claiming he had already paid his premium for a property in Linwood.
